    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>控制一只可爱的小猫，在充满魅力和挑战的旅程中，它会在经过的地方留下一条毛线！你的目标是用毛线覆盖场景中的所有方块，解决巧妙的谜题并克服障碍。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏提供了独特的体验，有些方块会限制小猫的移动方向，需要策略和规划才能前进。此外，使用传送门将小猫从一个方块传送到另一个方块，增加了额外的复杂性和乐趣。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>对于创意玩家，编辑器模式允许你创建并玩自己设计的关卡！使用游戏中所有可用的元素，如方向块、传送门和关卡终点，来设计独特的挑战。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这款游戏完美结合了可爱、策略和创意，非常适合爱猫人士、解谜爱好者以及喜欢自己设计挑战的玩家。准备好享受数小时轻松而刺激的乐趣吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索、撤销和传送！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/f9de781995c51ceda163f31b902457fc.poster.avif?t=1741823854\" width=750 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/f9de781995c51ceda163f31b902457fc.webm?t=1741823854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/f9de781995c51ceda163f31b902457fc.mp4?t=1741823854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小猫在场景中移动，必要时可以撤销步骤，并使用传送门在方块之间传送。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创意模式：创建、游玩并完成！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/0aa0d6ddf87b545c7bf41a5382d9e94e.poster.avif?t=1741823854\" width=750 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/0aa0d6ddf87b545c7bf41a5382d9e94e.webm?t=1741823854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/0aa0d6ddf87b545c7bf41a5382d9e94e.mp4?t=1741823854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将你的想法变为现实：按照自己的方式创建关卡，并测试你设计的每个关卡！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻松放置和删除方块！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/459ef64d4cbe8e6ff6e96c1ea890c6c3.poster.avif?t=1741823854\" width=750 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/459ef64d4cbe8e6ff6e96c1ea890c6c3.webm?t=1741823854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/459ef64d4cbe8e6ff6e96c1ea890c6c3.mp4?t=1741823854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建、调整并自定义你的关卡。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >切换游戏元素</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/b35b289fa4af6e940dee7ddb5cc63ccf.poster.avif?t=1741823854\" width=750 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/b35b289fa4af6e940dee7ddb5cc63ccf.webm?t=1741823854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/b35b289fa4af6e940dee7ddb5cc63ccf.mp4?t=1741823854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用Q键浏览所有可用的元素：移动块、方向块、传送门和关卡终点。</p>",
